author: GoPro
description:
This is every pilot's dream—flying in perfect formation alongside some of the most talented operators in the world in a stunning setting. This incredible scene was captured by our next-generation 360 action camera—GoPro MAX2.

Strap in with Flying Bulls' pilots Matthias Dolderer, Stefan Doblhammer, Dario Costa, as they take off from Red Bull's famous Hanger 7 airstrip in Salzburg, Austria in route to one of the most stunning sunrises you're ever seen over the Austrian Alps. Between the 3 of them, world championship titles, countless hours of flying, and nearly unlimited trust in each other's abilities to fly a one of these tricky stunt planes. Fasten your seatbelt + thank you for flying Air GoPro.
